        <Char_Desc_80>Experimental Windows PowerShell GUI archiver using STAR containers.</Char_Desc_80>
        <Char_Desc_250>SmartTAR STAR is an experimental Windows PowerShell archiver using tar.exe, STAR containers, SHA-256 verification and recovery-friendly design.</Char_Desc_250>
        <Char_Desc_450>SmartTAR STAR is an experimental Windows PowerShell GUI archiver focused on archive creation, verification and recovery workflows using tar.exe, STAR containers and SHA-256 validation.</Char_Desc_450>
        <Char_Desc_2000>SmartTAR STAR is an experimental Windows PowerShell GUI archiver from the eco-by-different project. It focuses on transparent archive containers, verification and recovery-friendly workflows. It uses tar.exe, STAR containers and SHA-256 validation. Supported modes include Hybrid, Smart, Solid and Smart XZ.</Char_Desc_2000>
